 <p><a id="TSJN-01-04-0667-kw-0001" class="keywordref" title="jump to Mr. Dunlap in text" href="#TSJN-01-04-0667-ks-0001">Mr. Dunlap</a>  <a id="TSJN-01-04-0667-kw-0002" class="keywordref" title="jump to Mr. Hays in text" href="#TSJN-01-04-0667-ks-0002">Mr. Hays</a>: John Dunlap and James Hayes, printers; see <a href="default.xqy?keys=TSJN-print-01-03-02-0677" class="document">TJ to the Virginia Delegates in Congress, 31 Aug. <span class="choice correction" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover_choice ] header=[]  body=[ Corrected from '1708' &lt;span style='font-size: 90%'&gt;[[2008-03-31]]&lt;/span&gt; ]">1780</span></a>; also <a href="default.xqy?keys=TSJN-print-01-04-02-0490" class="document">Hayes to TJ, 18</a>, <a href="default.xqy?keys=TSJN-print-01-04-02-0537" class="document">23 Jan</a>.; and the <a href="default.xqy?keys=TSJN-print-01-04-02-0858" class="document">Virginia Delegates letter to TJ, 20 Feb. 1781</a>.</p></div>
